Saturday glory.

'Un'ora al sole ti vorrei...'
(Remake invernale della foto estiva ''un'ora al mare ti vorrei'' remember?)

I'm particularly touched by this news, more than others. Maybe because it also involved his daughter, Gigi. I realize how unpredictable life is, right in these moments. I realize the importance of smiling in front of difficulties, even when I don't want to. Enjoying happy moments is also this. It's above all this. Do it for something you love and for those you love, is priceless. Do what you like at best, do it to the fullest, work hard, BE the best. Try to inspire people, whatever they want to do. This will make you feel good. Obsession is GOOD, in everything.
It was a dinner for two, I suppose.
